These are Puzzles for 2x6 Level 8

.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-8-1::.
The people use 6 different means of transport: jet-ski, tram, ship, snowmobile, quad-bike, helicopter
There are 6 different favourite beverages: hot-chocolate, tea, fanta, sprite, lemonade, cola
 1. the person drinking fanta is on the left of the person driving the jet-ski##1
 2. the person driving the tram is on the left or right of the person drinking tea##3
 3. the person driving the tram is somewhere to the right of the person drinking hot-chocolate##5
 4. the person drinking cola is not to the left of the person driving the ship##8
 5. the person driving the helicopter is somewhere to the right of the person drinking lemonade##5
 6. the person drinking lemonade is somewhere between the person drinking fanta and the person driving the helicopter##7
 7. the person driving the jet-ski is not to the left of the person drinking fanta##8
 8. the person driving the quad-bike is on the left or right of the person drinking tea##3
 9. the person driving the helicopter is on the left or right of the person driving the quad-bike##3
10. the person drinking hot-chocolate is not to the left of the person driving the snowmobile##8
11. the person drinking lemonade is somewhere to the right of the person driving the snowmobile##5
12. the person driving the tram is on the right of the person driving the snowmobile##1
13. the person driving the ship is somewhere to the right of the person drinking fanta##5
14. the person driving the helicopter is somewhere between the person drinking tea and the person driving the ship##7
15. the person drinking cola is somewhere to the right of the person drinking hot-chocolate##5
16. the person driving the quad-bike is not the person drinking sprite##6

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2    |   3    |   4   |       5        |   6   |
| Transport           | snowmobile | tram | jet-ski | quad-bike | helicopter | ship |
| Beverage   | hot-chocolate | fanta    | tea  | lemonade  | sprite            | cola  |

