 2. the person who likes coral is somewhere to the right of the person who's hobby is drawing##5
 3. the person who's hobby is singing is somewhere to the right of the person who likes emerald##5
 4. the person who's hobby is chess is not to the left of the person who likes coral##8
 5. the person who likes brown is somewhere to the left of the person who's hobby is singing##5
 6. the person who likes amber is on the left or right of the person who likes brown##3
 7. the person who's hobby is reading is somewhere to the right of the person who likes brown##5
 8. the person who likes grey is not to the right of the person who likes grey##8
 9. the person who likes white is somewhere to the right of the person who likes brown##5
10. the person who's hobby is sudoku is on the far right##1
11. the person who's hobby is singing is somewhere between the person who likes emerald and the person who's hobby is chess##7
12. the person who's hobby is drawing is somewhere to the left of the person who's hobby is chess##5
13. the person who likes amber is between the person who's hobby is magic-tricks and the person who's hobby is singing##2
14. the person who likes coral is on the right of the person who likes grey##1
15. the person who's hobby is chess is somewhere between the person who's hobby is singing and the person who likes white##7
16. the person who's hobby is magic-tricks is not to the left of the person who's hobby is magic-tricks##8
17. the person who's hobby is singing is somewhere to the right of the person who's hobby is magic-tricks##5
