 8. the person who's birthday is in september is not to the left of the person who's birthday is in august##8
 9. the person who's birthday is in july is on the left or right of the person traveling to prague##3
10. the person who's birthday is in january is not the person traveling to colone##6
11. the person who's birthday is in june is somewhere to the left of the person traveling to colone##5
12. the person who's birthday is in september is on the left or right of the person traveling to london##3
13. the person who's birthday is in january is not to the left of the person who's birthday is in april##8

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2    |   3    |     4      |     5     |    6     |
| City   | boston | venice | hannover  | london     | prague | colone |
| Birthday           | april        | august    | september | june | january     | july  |

